Number 10

19
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,730
Canned Air

20
00:00:46,730 --> 00:00:49,450
Sometimes, life imitates art.

21
00:00:49,450 --> 00:00:51,480
Spaceballs is art, right?

22
